        </div>

        <p>Annual billing typically saves 15–33%. Additional users and add-on modules cost extra. A free trial or money-back guarantee is available — verify the current terms on the official pricing page before purchase.</p>

        <h3>The real monthly cost most reviews skip</h3>
        <p>SpyFu hands you the data. It does not write, optimise, or publish anything. To actually run SEO with SpyFu's intelligence, here is the real monthly math:</p>

