        <h2 id="performance">Performance benchmarks — how SpyFu stacks up</h2>
        <p>SpyFu's signature dataset is the historical PPC ad database — <strong>every Google Ads keyword bought and ad copy variation tested since 2006</strong>. Semrush and Ahrefs show current ads. SpyFu shows the full history. The platform indexes 7.2T search results and tracks 152M websites. Backlink data is sparser and less fresh than Ahrefs. Rank tracking is accurate for US/UK markets, thinner internationally.</p>

        <h3>Historical PPC ad data depth</h3>

